item.title: CVE-2023-43081|2023-11-22T12:50:22.272Z -- dell -- powerprotect%20agent%20for%20file%20system
item.description: PowerProtect Agent for File System Version 19.14 and prior, contains an incorrect default permissions vulnerability in ddfscon component. A low Privileged local attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to overwriting of log files.
